Package restlib

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClientPreferences
    Client preferences that may be used by a server to perform content negotiation.
    ClientPreferencesBuilder
    A builder for generating instances of ClientPreference.
    ClientPreferencesWrapper
    An implementation of ClientPreferences which forwards all its method calls to another instance of ClientPreferences.
    ConnectionInfo
    Connection features of an HTTP request or response.
    ConnectionInfoBuilder
    A builder for generating instances of ConnectionInfo.
    ConnectionInfoWrapper
    An implementation of ConnectionInfo which forwards all its method calls to another instance of ConnectionInfo.
    ContentInfo
    Content properties of an HTTP message entity.
    ContentInfoBuilder
    A builder for generating instances of ContentInfo.
    ContentInfoWrapper
    An implementation of ContentInfo which forwards all its method calls to another instance of ContentInfo.
    Request
    Object representation of an HTTP Request.
    RequestBuilder
    A builder for generating Request instances.
    RequestPreconditions
    Preconditions sent by the client that determine if a request should be processed or not.
    RequestPreconditionsBuilder
    A builder for generating RequestPrecondition instances.
    RequestPreconditionsWrapper
    An implementation of RequestPreconditions which forwards all its method calls to another instance of RequestPreconditions.
    RequestWrapper
    An implementation of Request which forwards all its method calls to another instance of Request.
    Response
    Object representation of an HTTP Response.
    ResponseBuilder
    A builder for generating Response instances.
    ResponseWrapper
    An implementation of Response which forwards all its method calls to another instance of Response.
